        <item>
            <title>Version 0.9.14</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 18:15:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.9.14</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.9.14</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.2</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Per-segment voice re-check + SystemAudioBridge race fix</h3>
                <ul>
                <li>New: per-segment voice embedding re-check — catches longer (&gt;0.5s) diarizer misattributions that the splitter-level smoothing in v0.9.13 couldn't help with. Use Re-process on older recordings to apply.</li>
                <li>Phase-2 race condition fix in SystemAudioBridge — replaced NSLock with a serial dispatch queue; eliminates four concurrency bugs flagged in earlier reviews.</li>
                <li>Silent I/O errors in system-audio WAV writes now surface via OSLog.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
